text: Daphnella gracilis is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Raphitomidae.Worldwide Mollusc Species Data Base: Daphnella gracilis ==Description== The length of the shell attains 36.8 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species occurs in the East China Sea. ==References== gracilis Category:Gastropods described in 1952
title: Daphnella gracilis
